<figureCitation id="F0AC62D9FF8DFFDC3DD4FCB5FEE67384" box="[241,323,871,898]" captionStart="FIGURES 13–17" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1499,1523]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,1475]" captionTargetId="figure-18@16.[151,1436,181,1475]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 13–17. Type specimens of Australasian Mutillidae. 13. Ancistrotilla aenigmatica Brothers, 2012, ♂, holotype: ha- bitus dorsal view, habitus lateral view. 14. Mutilla aerata André, 1896, ♀, holotype: habitus dorsal view, habitus lateral view, labels. 15. Mutilla aeruginosa Smith, 1879, ♂, lectotype: habitus dorsal view, labels. 16. Mutilla affinis Westwood, 1843, ♀, holotype: habitus dorsal view, head dorsal view, habitus lateral view, labels. 17. Mutilla afflicta André, 1902, ♀, holotype: ha- bitus dorsal view, labels." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6572189" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6572189/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
